        <briefdescription>
<para>Global access point for services registered with the engine. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="class_boon_1_1_service_locator" kindref="compound">ServiceLocator</ref> stores a pointer to a <ref refid="class_boon_1_1_service_registry" kindref="compound">ServiceRegistry</ref> instance which holds runtime service singletons. Use Register/Get/Reset to manage services. Call <ref refid="class_boon_1_1_service_locator_1a631272ae5de4ef774a65f1391bb7e715" kindref="member">Shutdown()</ref> to clear all registered services. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
